	<h1 class="title">英文版推出一年后，中文版《成为乔布斯》终于要上市了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/37534/small/37534.JPG?1421809836" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">石玉 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-31 07:21:58 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/24730/medium/24730.jpg?1459339701" alt="" />			
